pageProduct.name: Swisse Iron + Probiotic 30 Tablets
pageProduct.description:
General Information

SWISSE ULTIBOOST IRON + PROBIOTIC is a premium quality formula containing 20 mg of iron, 16.5 mg of vitamin C and 2 Billion CFU of Bacillus coagulans.

 

Warnings

Not suitable for children. Bacillus coagulans may affect the way some medicines work, including immunosuppressants. Consult your health professional before taking with other medicines.

If symptoms persist, talk to your health professional.

Vitamin & mineral supplements should not replace a balanced diet.

If symptoms persist, talk to your health professional.

Vitamin supplements should not replace a balanced diet.

Common Uses

Gentle On Stomach: Iron amino acid chelate is a low-constipation, low-nausea form of iron that’s gentle on the stomach and helps prevent dietary iron deficiency.

Ingredients

Iron (from iron amino acid chelate)   20mg
Vitamin C (ascorbic acid)  16.5mg
Bacillus coagulans (MTCC No. 5260) (Unique IS2™)   2 billion CFU

Directions

DIRECTIONS FOR USE - ADULT DOSAGE:
One tablet daily, during or immediately after a meal, or as directed by a healthcare professional.
